
npx playwright test = to run all test cases
npx playwright test /path of test case = to run specific file of test cases
test.only = will run only this test case
npx playwright test --debug = to debug test case using playwright inspector tool
npx playwright codegen https://google.com (website to record and play test) = to record and playback test case
trace : 'only-on-failure' ,  = to generate trace only for fail test case 
npx playwright test --ui = its ui test runner to run test case in playwright runner